	     <h2>Inchirieri </h2>
		    <p class="alb"> Pretul de inchiriere al terenurilor difera in functie de intervalul orar al zilei</p>
			<p class="prog"> <strong> Program </strong> <br/> <strong> 07:00-23:00 </strong> </p>
			<table>
			   <caption> Program inchiriere terenuri </caption>
			     <thead> 
				   <tr> 
				     <th> Interval </th>
